  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7e822aad7b61dec47bb7b52e4276192f, type: 3}
  m_Name: Book1 1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Lines:
  - "Do you remember the \u201Che\u201D she mentioned in her diary?"
  - "That was your mother\u2019s assistant."
  - "He tried to use his position to steal your mother\u2019s inventions."
  - "That\u2019s exactly why I told you that your mother is too kind and often gets
    taken advantage of. "
  - "What your mom didn\u2019t tell you is that this assistant was trying to use
    this technology to commit the perfect crime, because teleportation can create
    a near-perfect alibi."
  - Your mom is a person of strong principles; she originally invented this to help
    others, not to harm them.
  - So as soon as she discovered this, she immediately kicked the assistant out of
    the lab.
  - But she was worried he might seek revenge on you, so she chose to leave you behind.
  ReplyOptions:
  - line: I feel so sad.
    nextNode: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 7f260a750da83a048b3244100e1193ef, type: 2}
    favorChange: 0
    requiredFavor: -10
    endDialogue: 0
    playerLine: I can't imagine how much pressure my mom must have been under when
      she made that decision.
